---
title: "US33 — View full workout history"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>HistoryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ViewWorkoutHistory
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession
  A->>B: open History tab
  B->>C: load sessions
  C->>E: listEndedSessions(userId, from: lifetime)
  note right of E: Premium — no date bound,<br/>Free month-cap not applied
  E-->>C: List (every WorkoutSession)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (full grouped history)
  B-->>A: every recorded session
  note over E: listEndedSessions via WorkoutGateway → Supabase (RLS)
